text: Ehsan Abdelmalek (born 27 November 1986) is an Egyptian female handball player who plays for Nice Handball and the Egypt national team. ==Achievements== *Coupe de la Ligue: **Finalist: 2016 ==References== Category:Egyptian female handball players Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Egyptian expatriates in France
